02:14.868 --> 02:16.962
Just show us where we can find
this Fonzie guy, okay?

02:17.104 --> 02:18.594
Hey, Pots, get a load of this.

02:18.739 --> 02:20.764
"Jack Duvall, talent scout,
Paramount Pictures, Hollywood."

02:20.908 --> 02:22.239
This guy's on the level!

02:22.376 --> 02:23.810
- Hollywood?!
- All right, I do comedy.

02:23.944 --> 02:25.503
