Good evening, ladies and germs.

02:29.083 --> 02:30.573
How do you like me so far?

02:30.718 --> 02:32.550
- You're doing great, Malph.
- I know, I still got it.

02:32.686 --> 02:34.677
Yeah, well, and I sing.
I sing real good.

