03:20.234 --> 03:21.326
That's Fonzie.

03:21.468 --> 03:22.936
Oh, no, no,
don't worry about it, chief.

03:23.070 --> 03:24.128
I'll-I'll take care of it.

03:24.271 --> 03:26.330
